response.original_title: Garech De Brun: Last Days At Lugalla
response.overview: An intimate film looking back at the life and career of Garech Browne, one of the most acclaimed modern patrons of the arts and Irish culture. His sudden death in 2018 left a gap in the diversity of Irish culture, but in that wake lies a yarn of stories that offer a unique insight into the man.
response.title: Garech De Brun: Last Days At Lugalla
